        <div class="insight-box">
            <h3>Strategic Implication</h3>
            <p>Understanding these patterns allows MMT advocates to guide conversations toward productive outcomes rather than getting trapped in predictable loops. The goal isn't winning arguments, but moving conversations beyond paradigm conflicts.</p>
